name: Digital Angst
description:
The digitalization of life often impacted as if there are clear metrics and numbers of a person ‘reputation’. Likes, comments, engagement rates and sales now could be seen blatantly. It is not a secret that many artists in the NFTs community struggling with their mental health, especially at the start at their career, when the sales is low, while on the other hand the self-expectation on the all time high. 

At the start of the piece, I tried to picture those insecure and competitive feelings, but I’m struggling to picture it perfectly. It really hard to create the sketch and base of it, but then at uncertain point, I felt like unveil a picture of a new unique feelings which I can’t describe in textual manner. Maybe a set of words like blues, uneasy, angst and upset is close to describe it, even though at some point I feel like it doesn’t fully fit perfectly.

Oil digital painting
PNG 3500 x 4950 px
